The most complete Gloomhaven mod on TTS. Just load this and you're good to go.

Isaac approved. :)

[h1]tl;dr?[/h1]

[i]Included:[/i]

[b]Everything[/b] in the box, and then some.

All in-box classes (including unlockables), with minis
All monsters & bosses, ditto
All main campaign, solo (including unlockables), No Pun Included (NPI), Into the Unknown, [i]and[/i] just-released Capital Intrigue scenarios (1 - 3)
Most sealed content
Full rulebook, terrain, map, map stickers, achievements, etc etc.

Note: solo scenarios are stored inside the class enveleopes (in the level 5 nested envelope), to prevent spoilers.

Some of the assets in this mod are in fact based on Gloomhaven's pre-release or 1st print, not 2nd. This should be fixed soon.

[h1]How is this mod different from all other mods?[/h1]

This is a remix and customization of multiple other mods, content from BGG, and custom content.

The intent is to be a 100% complete Gloomhaven mod, focused on quality of life improvements to make the gameplay easier & faster, and making unlockable content unlock naturally (rather than being based on not reading parts of the page or cross-referencing lookup tables). A lot is WIP, but it already includes all available TTS Gloomhaven content - and then some. It's fully playable, and starts already set up for your first campaign. Just create your characters, set up the first scenario, and enjoy. :-)

[i]New, customized, and/or added content vs other mods[/i]

Gameplay:
* Capital Intrigue
* Into the Unknown (w/ staging pre-prepared, WIP)
* No Pun Included (NPI)
* Solo scenarios & items (incl. for unlockable classes)
* Decoder card
* Sealed envelopes
* Town records book (back-translated)

Setup:
* 4-player table w/ two hands per player, extended & colored player areas
* All content reuploaded to Steam cloud for faster & more reliable loading
* Character & monster envelopes w/ minis, sleeves, etc. included; nested unlocks for classes
* Gloomhaven visiting board w/ sanctuary donation counting bowl
* Monster stat sheets w/ integrated stateful sleeves (level 0 is the highest state #, e.g. 8)
* Monster trackers for regular / elite and #
* Official FAQ (redacted version); unredacted (spoilerific) version in locked chest inside unlockables chest (pending componentization)
* Retiree holder & form
* Rule summaries & monster AI flowchart
* Special conditions for opening envelopes form
* Stateful, infinite-bag map & terrain tiles
* Stateful, hideable treasure index
* Stateful, locked containers
* Tri-color Bar Keep (red / blue / yellow) for HP bars, with wide variant option
* Useful tools from across TTS
* Unlockable content separated from starting content
* Various tweaks to make it Just Work (and help prevent spoilers)
... and full integration of more or less all other TTS Gloomhaven mods' content.

